  <name translate="no">MasVisGtk</name>
  <summary translate="no">Audio analysis tool for your music</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Detect audio mastering defects. Based on pymasvis app/module, using numpy, scipy, pyplot (matplotlib).</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Waveform plotting</li>
        <li>Overview of files (by-folder support)</li>
        <li>Frequency plot</li>
        <li>Dynamic Range estimation</li>
        <li>Peak estimation</li>
        <li>Crest Factor estimation</li>
        <li>Histogram plot</li>
        <li>Peak vs. RMS plot</li>
        <li>Loudness analysis, EBU R128 plot</li>
        <li>Multi-channel audio support</li>
      </ul>
  </description>
